%p
	CSV should contain the following columns, named exactly as follows(order is not important):
	%ul
		%li SCIPER
		%li name
		%li email
		%li role
		%li studio(may be left empty)
%p 
	If the studio does not exist, it will be automatically created. If the user already exists, 
	%em it will be updated to the values present in the csv!

= form_tag users_upload_post_path(), multipart: true do
	= file_field_tag :users_csv
	= hidden_tag :year_id, value: @year.id
	= submit_tag "Submit", class: "ui button"